<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug which caused a Shaper to become stuck in a falling animation when pulled by this ability while they were falling.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32.1 (July 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Passive - Double-Edge</b></li><ul><li>Kahgen now gains double the amount of Focus from his basic attacks when attacking enemy Shapers.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Quicksand (W)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where enemies on the outer edge of the Quicksand zone were being slowed for less than the intended amount.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28.1 (April 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Dust Devil (Q)</b></li><ul><li>The Focus cost to use this ability has been reduced to 30, down from 40.</li></ul><li><b>The Big Haul (R)</b></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 120/110/100, down from 140/130/120.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28 (April 8, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The recommended items on Kahgen have been updated.</li><li><b>Dust Devil (Q)</b></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 3 seconds at all ranks, down from 4.</li><li>The base damage of this ability has been increased to 40/65/90/115/150, up from 35/60/85/110/135.</li><li>The base damage per stack of Spirit Sands that a target is affected by has been increased to 10/15/20/25/30, up from 6/9/12/15/18.</li><li>The Power ratio per stack of Spirit Sand has been increased to 0.15, up from 0.08.</li></ul><li><b>Heat Wave (E)</b></li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased to 540, up from 500.</li></ul></ul>